  <brief_title>OPT-80 in Clostridium Difficile-Associated Diarrhea (CDAD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label, Dose Ranging, Randomized Clinical Evaluation of OPT-80 in Patients With Clostridium Difficile-Associated Diarrhea (CDAD)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
